Package grafioschtrader.gtnet

Enum Class GTNetMessageCodeType

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<GTNetMessageCodeType>
grafioschtrader.gtnet.GTNetMessageCodeType
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<GTNetMessageCodeType>, Constable
public enum GTNetMessageCodeType extends Enum<GTNetMessageCodeType>
Enums ending with C are intended for communication triggering by the client. Enums ending with S are intended as a response from the server. Enums containing a _SEL_ are applied to the remote server. Enums that have an _ALL_ will be applied to all remote servers that are affected.
